OL,6,FTeenagers as young as 18 will be able
OL,7,Fto drive trains as part of new
OL,8,Fgovernment proposals aimed at easing
OL,9,Fstaffing shortages,
OL,11,FThe Department for Transport is
OL,12,Fproposing to reduce the minimum age
OL,13,Ffor driving a train on Britain's
OL,14,Frailways from 20 to 18.
OL,16,FThe plans could be put in place as
OL,17,Fearly as this summer.
